#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:191
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the toolbar, the main component of the Layers panel is the "
"frame listing all the layers added to the project, optionally organized in "
"groups. A layer with a checked box next to it displays its contents "
"overlapping the map canvas extent, unless a :ref:`scale-based visibility "
